<div class="mw-heading mw-heading3"><h3 id="Yeung_Kin_Man_Academic_Building_(YEUNG)"><span id="Yeung_Kin_Man_Academic_Building_.28YEUNG.29"></span>Yeung Kin Man Academic Building (YEUNG)</h3><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=City_University_of_Hong_Kong&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3" title="Edit section: Yeung Kin Man Academic Building (YEUNG)"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div><p>
Yeung Kin Man Academic Building, formerly known as Academic 1,<sup id="cite&#95;ref-17" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-17"><span class="cite-bracket">&#91;</span>17<span class="cite-bracket">&#93;</span></a></sup> was also called "Academic Building"<sup id="cite&#95;ref-18" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-18"><span class="cite-bracket">&#91;</span>18<span class="cite-bracket">&#93;</span></a></sup><sup id="cite&#95;ref-19" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-19"><span class="cite-bracket">&#91;</span>19<span class="cite-bracket">&#93;</span></a></sup><sup id="cite&#95;ref-20" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-20"><span class="cite-bracket">&#91;</span>20<span class="cite-bracket">&#93;</span></a></sup><sup id="cite&#95;ref-21" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-21"><span class="cite-bracket">&#91;</span>21<span class="cite-bracket">&#93;</span></a></sup> before the completion of Academic 2. It was completed in stages from 1989 to 1994. The floor area is 63,000&#160;<a href="/wiki/Square_metre" title="Square metre">m<sup>2</sup></a> (680,000&#160;<a href="/wiki/Square_foot" title="Square foot">sq&#160;ft</a>), and includes 116 laboratories, 18 lecture halls, classrooms and canteens. The building is divided by colour, in order of purple zone (P), green zone (G), blue zone (B), yellow zone (Y) and red zone (R). Except for the lecture halls, all classrooms and laboratories are numbered by their colour divisions.</p><ul class="gallery mw-gallery-traditional">
	<li class="gallerycaption">Yeung Kin Man Academic Building, CityU</li>
		<li class="gallerybox" style="width: 155px">
			<div class="thumb" style="width: 150px; height: 150px;"><span typeof="mw:File"><a href="/wiki/File:C01-086.jpg" class="mw-file-description" title="Entrance to YKM Academic Building"><img alt="Entrance to YKM Academic Building" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/aa/C01-086.jpg/120px-C01-086.jpg" decoding="async" width="120" height="80" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/aa/C01-086.jpg/250px-C01-086.jpg 2x" data-file-width="2100" data-file-height="1400" /></a></span></div>
			<div class="gallerytext">Entrance to YKM Academic Building</div>
		</li>
